These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-1::.
7 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, goldfish, chinchilla, mouse, rabbit, hamster
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cycling, water-polo, baseball, rugby, sailing, cricket, rowing
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 2. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the owner of the goldfish##8
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
 4. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
 5. the owner of the bird is not to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##8
 6. the owner of the bird is not the person who's sport is water-polo##6
 7. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
 8. the owner of the mouse is not to the left of the owner of the hamster##8
 9. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere between the person who's sport is rowing and the person who's sport is water-polo##7
10. the person who's sport is water-polo is the owner of the rabbit##1
11. the owner of the rabbit is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
13. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
14. the owner of the hamster is somewhere between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is cycling##7
15. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
16. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the left of the owner of the mouse##8
17. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5
18. the owner of the hamster is the person who's sport is baseball##1
19. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
20. the owner of the chinchilla is not the person who's sport is cricket##6
21. the owner of the bird is not to the right of the owner of the bird##8
22. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |      3       |    4    |    5     |      6      |    7    |
| Pet           | rabbit | goldfish | hamster | ferret  | mouse  | chinchilla | bird    |
| Sport   | water-polo   | cycling   | baseball   | rugby | sailing | rowing        | cricket |

