.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: zombie, scientific, documentary, disaster, horror, drama, time-travel
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cycling, swimming, biathlon, lacrosse, climbing, basketball, badminton
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is in the middle##1
 2. the person who's sport is basketball is not the person watching documentary movies##6
 3. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 4. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person watching documentary movies##2
 5. the person watching horror movies is in an odd position##4
 6. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 7. the person watching time-travel movies is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##8
 9. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching disaster movies##5
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
11. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
12. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##8
13. the person watching disaster movies is not to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##8
14. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5
15. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
16. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
