 5. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
 6. the bongani-smoker is the townhouse house##1
 7. the art-deco house is on the far right##1
 8. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the left of the cape-cod house##5
 9. the blend-smoker is not to the left of the townhouse house##8
